      <h1>Plant sales</h1>

      <p>Our nursery is open from March to the end of June, every morning from 9:30 am to noon, including Sundays and public holidays. We offer young plants to grow in your garden or greenhouse. These are mainly plants for culinary use: edible flowers, heritage vegetables, seasonings and aromatics, herbal teas, tropical aromatics, sweet-making plants and assorted salads.</p>

